{
  "stem": "16163.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had Jewish words which we used, I think, I remember, but not that we spoke really Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had a river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a river.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as little children, we would go swimming there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that later on, we couldn't do that anymore either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were not many things we could do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Germans, by the town, by the burgomeister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think we'd maybe have gone swimming till 1937, '38.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after that, it was nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 1936 maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a movie which we could not attend to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a big sign up that Jews couldn't-- were not allowed to go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember my mother taking me to another town to see a movie.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the middle of one of the movies, it got dark.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They turned off the screen, and announced that now that there are Jews in the movie house, and they should leave.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had to leave in the middle of the performance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That must have been about-- I think it was maybe 1936, '37 already, because after '38, we couldn't even leave the town anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it must have been in 1936, '37.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there were-- we were in a different town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were different Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was way of life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the towns are so small that every-- you know, and so near each other, that everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I mean, I was a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did what my mother told me to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I walked out with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember meeting other people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother acknowledged them, and they acknowledged us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
